<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee3af2f3-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s504"><num value="504">§ 504.</num><heading> “Person” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The word “person” as used in this chapter shall be held to embrace also any partnership, corporation, association, or other legal entity.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee3af2f4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1929-01-14/ch69/s4">Jan. 14, 1929, ch. 69, § 4</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/45/1080">45 Stat. 1080</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
